                     divide 100           into w-prn-liv-det-cun
           else      go to prn-liv-det-100.
           go to     prn-liv-det-100.
       prn-liv-det-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione valore totale                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           multiply  w-sdp-tot-dpz        by   w-prn-liv-det-cun
                                        giving w-prn-liv-det-val      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento area totali                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se flag di costo determinato indica Non de- *
      *                  * terminato, si incrementa il contatore ge-   *
      *                  * nerale elementi non valorizzati             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prn-liv-det-fcd    =    spaces
                     add   1              to   w-tot-gen-cen          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo ordinamento *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tip-ord-tip-ord    =    01 or
                     w-tip-ord-tip-ord    =    02
                     go to prn-liv-det-110
           else if   w-tip-ord-tip-ord    =    03 or
                     w-tip-ord-tip-ord    =    04
                     go to prn-liv-det-120.
       prn-liv-det-110.
